snippet.title: PSO - Episode 4 (a.k.a. PSOBB) - True Intro
snippet.description:
The true original intro of Phantasy Star Online Episode 4 a.k.a. Phantasy Star Blue Burst on the PC.
This original intended intro was replaced by the slideshow intro to save space. (PSOBB was downloadable)


© Sonic Team / Sega 2004/2005
